{"tid":772193,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人大左自己個人好似愈黎愈冷血","createTime":"2018-08-08T14:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T04:27:04.000Z","uid":191555,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4514e4615ab2867aff03b818bb9b2ccadcfe114e","tid":772193,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"自從出左黎做野<br />\n同女朋友散左幾年到現在<br />\n個人真係對好多野失去左興趣咁<br />\n對好多事都開始有個諗法係視而不見算....<br />\n對朋友/家人都好冷淡<br />\n<br />\n不過又未到會想自尋既時候(自問自己都幾撚怕死)<br />\n<br />\n生活&gt;工作&gt;瞓<br />\n<br />\n日復一日，對生活無熱情<br />\n<br />\n係得旅行有意慾<br />\n<br />\n一個人去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b07d3b7c9af1b61822df637a11583237d9ef15","tid":772193,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講曬我心聲"},{"pid":"5746daa372c8b5943d5c9103c7b78ba1634be6c5","tid":772193,"uid":19604,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:47:52.000Z","msg":"中意去旅行又話冷血"},{"pid":"035083efca4108854c2fe2bab59b325acef1dc15","tid":772193,"uid":67182,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩叫冷血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d121a218669c48a604588a64ba28d47e07551466","tid":772193,"uid":6294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:03:26.000Z","msg":"成年既生活係比童年平淡<br />\n安於現狀又唔等於冷血既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c9f6d1f0492f4dad4fc5b3265bd653853b271a","tid":772193,"uid":60451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:05:34.000Z","msg":"你係對生活失去熱情唔係冷血呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf156ff8d4675aaf39421b576b67f1afa39a4dbe","tid":772193,"uid":69256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"90c9f6d1f0492f4dad4fc5b3265bd653853b271a","tid":7721